---
const title = "Address The Mess | djerhy.tech";
const description = "The 30 day authority sprint for mapping ownership, decision rights, and operational control across systems.";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description}>

  <meta property="og:title" content={title}>
  <meta property="og:description" content={description}>
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">

  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">

  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #0D1117;
      color: #e6edf3;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    header {
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.12);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 650;
      color: #e6edf3;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    nav a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b1bac4;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover { color: #e6edf3; }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 46px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #b1bac4;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .subnote {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #9aa4af;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #9aa4af;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin: 40px 0 14px 0;
    }

    .resource-card {
      display: block;
      background: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.035);
      border: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.10);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .resource-card:hover {
      background: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.055);
      border-color: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.18);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .resource-card-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .resource-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e6edf3;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .resource-badge {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 750;
      color: #b1bac4;
      background: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.12);
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .resource-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #b1bac4;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .featured-card {
      background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.28);
    }

    .featured-card:hover {
      background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.11);
      border-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.40);
    }

    .featured-card .resource-badge {
      background: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.18);
      border-color: rgba(47, 129, 247, 0.34);
      color: #7fb0ff;
    }

    .helper-box {
      margin-top: 18px;
      background: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.10);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px 18px;
      color: #b1bac4;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .helper-box strong { color: #e6edf3; }

    .contact {
      margin-top: 52px;
      padding-top: 36px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.12);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b1bac4;
    }

    .contact a { color: #2F81F7; text-decoration: none; }
    .contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    footer {
      padding-top: 36px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.12);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9aa4af;
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .footer-identity { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    footer a { color: #b1bac4; text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: #e6edf3; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container { padding: 32px 16px; }
      h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .resource-card-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="logo">djerhy.tech</a>
      <nav>
        <a href="/start-here">Start Here</a>
        <a href="/resources">Resources</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h1>Address The Mess: The 30 Day Authority Sprint</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        A structured 30 day process for mapping ownership, decision rights, and operational control across a real system in your environment.
      </p>

      <p class="subnote">
        The goal is a defensible internal outcome you can hand to leadership after four weeks of contained work.
      </p>

      <div class="section-label">Start Here</div>

      <a href="https://2279442040293.gumroad.com/l/sjmcby" class="resource-card featured-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div class="resource-card-header">
          <div class="resource-title">Run the 30 Day Authority Sprint</div>
          <div class="resource-badge">Gumroad</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-desc">
          Identify ownership, verify dependencies, review access, and document what can safely change. Includes templates and outcome summary.
        </div>
      </a>

      <div class="helper-box">
        <strong>Outcome:</strong> you end the month able to explain who owns the system, who can access it, what depends on it, and what change would be risky.
      </div>

      <div class="section-label">Supporting Materials</div>

      <a href="/asset-walkthrough.pdf" class="resource-card" download>
        <div class="resource-card-header">
          <div class="resource-title">Field Exercise: Asset Discovery</div>
          <div class="resource-badge">PDF</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-desc">
          Exercise for locating unmanaged or unowned systems and documenting what you can verify.
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/Week One Security Assetment.pdf" class="resource-card" download>
        <div class="resource-card-header">
          <div class="resource-title">Week One Investigation</div>
          <div class="resource-badge">PDF</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-desc">
          A starting process for understanding operational exposure before implementing controls.
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/ATM2.pdf" class="resource-card" download>
        <div class="resource-card-header">
          <div class="resource-title">Diagnostic Prompts</div>
          <div class="resource-badge">PDF</div>
        </div>
        <div class="resource-desc">
          Questions used to surface ownership gaps and risky unknown dependencies.
        </div>
      </a>

      <div class="contact">
        Questions? <a href="mailto:contact@djerhy.tech">contact@djerhy.tech</a>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="footer-identity">
        Djerhy Jn Baptiste • CISSP
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/djerhyjnbaptiste" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/JBDjerhy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
        <a href="https://www.credly.com/users/djerhy-jn-baptiste" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Credly</a>
      </div>
      <div>© 2026 djerhy.tech</div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
